  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until charred, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the canned kidney beans, tomato paste, apple cider vinegar, honey, dried oregano, salt, and black pepper to the skillet. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the steel cut oats to the skillet and stir to combine with the other ingredients.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes, until the oats are lightly toasted.",
    "Warm the ti-leaf wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the wraps by spooning the oat mixture onto the center of each wrap.",
    "Drizzle the Turbinado sugar glaze over the top of each wrap.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
